Why Make the Shift?





















SAVE TIME

Complete your online employee schedules faster than ever so that you can spend more time with customers. Reduce time spent scheduling by 70%.






















REDUCE CONFUSION
Say goodbye to scheduling conflicts and miscommunication that cause missed shifts and unsatisfied customers. Keep everyone up-to-date via texts, notifications, alerts & emails.





















UPDATE SCHEDULES FAST
Stop scrambling to make and communicate last second schedule changes. Review, approve, publish, and communicate schedule changes instantly.























