Online Time & Attendance Software | Pricing Comparison





















































































Orbital Shift Product Comparison

Some new Orbital Shift customers are sure which of our products is best for their company’s labor management needs. For some organizations, it makes sense to choose our online work schedule product. It helps improve employee scheduling efficiency and alleviate the stress and headaches that often accompany the scheduling process. Other companies prefer to incorporate our mobile time clock solution with our scheduling software as a means of empowering managers to track and monitor real expenses in real time. A closer comparison of the two workforce management solutions can help you make the most intelligent choice for your company.








No-Risk Free Trial















Used & Loved by Thousands - Make Your Shift Today!
















 
"We had a very organized system in place but Orbital Shift still saves me time each week. It is an extremely affordable option, especially when you consider access, programming, and the exceptional customer service they provide."  Dan Monahan, Director of Operations - Double Tree Hotel



Overview of Our Labor Scheduling Software Features
Feature of our online work scheduler include:

Shift scheduling online
Shift cover management
Shift event templates
Copy and paste schedules
Email and text alerts
Custom event tags
Employee event reports
The ability to submit and manage employee requests
Conflict and overtime warnings
Event management via text and email
Labor budgets by location or department
Daily, weekly and monthly schedule views
Mobile optimized site













Our Online Employee Time Clock Software Offers a Host of Additional Features
When you select our online time and attendance software product you get all of the above plus:

Real-time labor tracking
Advanced exporting with time clock data
Enhanced budgeting with time clock data
Custom settings for time clock locations
Custom clock-out value
Notification of employees who forget to clock out
The ability to manage alerts when employees are late
Control over where and how employees clock in




What About the Cost?
Whether you choose our shift management software or mobile time clock solution, you’re assured of getting a product that will fit your budget. The monthly cost of our scheduling software is only $2 per user, with a minimum requirement of five users.
Our mobile time clock software costs only $3 per user per month, again with a minimum requirement of five users. This scalable, subscription-based pricing structure makes our software solutions affordable for small businesses, SMBs and large corporations alike.
 
Other Important Product Similarities
No matter which Orbital Shift software product you select, we know you’ll find it to be simple and intuitive to use. There’s no lengthy learning curve, and you don’t need to be a technical genius to use it with speed and efficiency.
We also provide world-class customer support for all of our products. And you won’t have to enter into a long-term contract or purchase pricey software or hardware additions.
 
Get Started Right Now With Our Free Trial Offer
Our online time and attendance and scheduling software both come with a free trial offer. Use the product for 14 days at no cost and without risk. Discover how our software solutions can save you time and money. Get started on your free trial today!


